                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bigmiao/">老喵</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-10-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">太学术</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="539176574">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-539176574" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-539176574" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="539176574">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Nataliecarol/">千軍萬馬式摸魚</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-06-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">李泽厚这三部曲，无论立论还是推演，鄙人都颇觉大有问题，只是有开风气之先的作用吧</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="567220135">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-567220135" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-567220135" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="567220135">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chorevorak/">柴到中年碎碎念</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读过会发现那个时期思潮的重要性，它们甚至至今都还影响深刻。但很多思潮运动进行得不够彻底，依然没有脱离开封建思想和一些传统形式的束缚。李泽厚先生在著这系列书时，感觉流畅性和引导性远不如《美的历程》。不过依然是好书，至少这是中国的第一套思潮史专著。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

